data.description: This country styled home is situated admist the white spruce forest above Goldstream valley on two landscaped acres at the end of Woodbine Drive. it has a long list of special features both interior and exterior such as two rock fireplaces concrete foundations (basement), main floors built with 6” x6” log then furred out interiors.  Main floor Has radiant heat and tile floors, upstairs has three bedrooms two with hardwood flooring and master with carpet. Home has new roof and new boiler  Shop is 20’ x 20’ constructed 2” x6” and covered with steel with 17’ door currently unheated
